opo經上次一役之後，戰術必有改善，<br />\n<br />\n而且中大一戰，popo只派一水炮車，<br />\n對比今次(一水炮、二鋭武、音波炮），而且旺角與poly非常近，所以加上旺角警力，可説popo今次差唔多總動員到poly<br />\n<br />\n另外學校報警、示威者取危險物品、使用弓箭、巨型亞叉等，popo可以此藉口，全面進入校園拘捕或使用致命武力。這必令各手足有慘重傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為popo正等待夜晚，街上人流減少，然後開戰。<br />\n<br />\n各前線手足，如果popo有任何唔妥，請唔好留，唔好送頭，唔好受傷，我哋一個都不能少。<br />\n<br />\n其他人，可選擇各區花、到中環集會或到poly支援。"},{"pid":"67785ce333a87005cfc73aa0c01f0bfe263c209c","tid":1729811,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:14:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc888b39fa5ca42d5def94d9a52940e536db1d3e","tid":1729811,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:18:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35c6775c9c2f22b292b57db6db6addabe6bce9d2","tid":1729811,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:18:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42e8737c53972536a95202d7f9687f9871f0cf58","tid":1729811,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:19:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffca99a505a8971e3f8315b484f661468d74d3c7","tid":1729811,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:19:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31c84e9da800fe30c31f6eec9a25ea72181b7e1d","tid":1729811,"uid":247027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:20:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8856ac3f730cca7c737551fe32b24fd14e123e48","tid":1729811,"uid":228319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:22:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"975f4961e0c7ab2dcb8e27ffc813e6a3cf4c2b20","tid":1729811,"uid":228319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:22:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c3ccc03ad2c15b57f70f08cacae78bc14d30559","tid":1729811,"uid":223219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:22:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca0ba3cd19176a55e7dd88dbe1bae7b5de15b933","tid":1729811,"uid":222264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime